numtrials|100|Number of trials to use. Note that there are 40 cards in each deck=120, and so cards get rotated without being shuffled if used up
DelayBetweenTrials|500|How long between trials, in which the feedback appears.
DelayWithBeep|0|Whether to give audio feedback between trials.  Feedback is a buzz and a 'kaching' sound
UseMouse|1|Should we use the mouse  (use 1; use 0 for the keyboard)?
shuffledecks|0|whether decks should be shuffled.  Shuffling happens in epochs of size 10, to maintain the reward structure within sets of 10.   The default is off
startvalue|2000|Starting money
